						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in a street in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Pramōdūta, Māgha śu. 5, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the construction of a well at Mallavōlu. Mentions Peddabba and Chelamma. In characters of the 15th century A.D.</p>						

